{"tid":1822690,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"26歲男瑞和街電競中心傷人 判監30個月 (案件編號：DCCC 142/2018)","createTime":"2020-01-13T06:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T16:18:49.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9bfd74f1bba4a76542e2f5f6dafe21b298652f","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"DCCC 142/2018<br />\n[2019] HKDC 1023<br />\n香港特別行政區<br />\n區域法院<br />\n刑事案件2018年第142號<br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n  香港特別行政區  <br />\n  訴  <br />\n  馮罡  <br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n主審法官： 區域法院暫委法官鄭念慈<br />\n日期： 2019年7月30日<br />\n出席人士：<br />\n馬詠璋女士，為外聘律師，代表香港特別行政區<br />\n李祖詒先生，由法律援助署委派的鄧耀榮律師行延聘，代表被告人<br />\n<br />\n控罪： [2] 有意圖而傷人（Wounding with intent）<br />\n---------------------<br />\n判刑理由書<br />\n---------------------<br />\n<br />\n1.  被告人承認一項有意圖而傷人罪，違反香港法例第212章《侵害人身罪條例》第17（a）條，他同意案情，裁定罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n案情<br />\n<br />\n2.  2017年9月15日，張家潤（控方第一證人）與朋友在一間位於觀塘瑞和街名為J@Net的電競中心玩電腦遊戲。期間，他因小事與被告人嘈交，被告人其後離開，控方第一證人繼續遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n3.  至凌晨四時許，被告人折返，<span style=\"color: red;\">先向距離控方第一證人約2米位置的牆壁擲下一玻璃樽，其後取出一把約一呎長的刀指向控方第一證人。</span>控方第一證人相信被告人會以刀砍他，於是上前試圖搶走該把刀。<span style=\"color: red;\">糾纏期間，被告人以刀砍了控方第一證人腿部一下。控方第一證人之後用手握著刀刃。</span><br />\n<br />\n4.  大概於同一時間，有另一男子到達，試圖勒住控方第一證人的頸，但不成功。<span style=\"color: red;\">其後，控方第一證人成功搶去被告人的刀，但該男子又搶走控方第一證人手上的刀，並將之帶離現場。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被告人亦停止與控方第一證人的糾纏，並且離開。控方第一證人受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n5.  根據醫療報告，<span style=\"color: red;\">控方第一證人右手中指有一處3厘米深的裂傷，筋腱被割傷，右手無名指與尾指、上腹部及右大腿一帶有多處表面裂傷。</span>"},{"pid":"8048339a534fc9d47987e74eb27114cad0be6d7b","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:13:43.000Z","msg":"被告人的背景及求情<br />\n<br />\n6.  被告人26歲，香港出世，接受教育至中三程度，未婚，獨自居住，曾於遊輪工作，月入約15,000至20,000元。<span style=\"color: red;\">他有五次出庭紀錄，其中有九項定罪紀錄，包括搶劫、盜竊、藏有攻擊性武器等，但沒有傷人的前科。</span><br />\n<br />\n7.  本席考慮了李大律師呈交的案例，包括HKSAR v Chan Chun Tat [2013] 6 HKC 225、香港特別行政區訴曾重新（DCCC 677/2018）及香港特別行政區訴林昭溜（DCCC 1078/2018）。<br />\n<br />\n8.  有意圖而傷人罪並沒有判刑指引，判刑視乎有關案情，一般刑期由3年至12年不等。根據香港特別行政區訴馬迪倫（CACC 112/2013）案，上訴庭曾引述Chan Chun Tat案，重申有意圖而傷人罪的嚴重性，判刑必須具阻嚇性。法庭須考慮的重要因素包括：<br />\n（1） 襲擊的預謀程度；<br />\n（2） 襲擊的背後動機；<br />\n（3） 襲擊者的精神狀態；<br />\n（4） 襲擊者有否受酒精或藥物影響；<br />\n（5） 襲擊是個人或群體行為；<br />\n（6） 使用的武器性質；<br />\n（7） 武力使用的程度；<br />\n（8） 受害人的傷勢；<br />\n（9） 襲擊帶給受害人（及親人等）的影響。"},{"pid":"8b8c4f36f3ded0c145b496e1544f64d58af5eb6e","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:14:10.000Z","msg":"9.  本席認為被告人是有一定程度的預謀犯案。他與控方第一證人嘈交後先行離去，<span style=\"color: red;\">折返時已帶備了一把刀，屬於可致命的武器。雖然被告人所使用的刀並不十分之長，但當時他顯然向手無寸鐵的控方第一證人施襲，但慶幸事件中沒有造成控方第一證人永久傷殘。而據控方第一證人當其時的傷勢顯示，相對並不十分嚴重。</span><br />\n<br />\n判刑<br />\n<br />\n10.  本席考慮了本案的案情、被告人的背景及控方第一證人的傷勢，採納3年9個月監禁（即45個月監禁）為量刑起點。被告人承認控罪，本席給予三分一判刑折扣，判監2年6個月（即30個月監禁）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  （ 鄭念慈 ）<br />\n  區域法院暫委法官"},{"pid":"9948b12b9ff74352d87f924e13a32c7ab189e761","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"<em>第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n17.意圖造成身體嚴重傷害而射擊、企圖射擊、傷人或打人<br />\n任何人意圖使任何人受殘害、外貌毀損、成為傷殘或身體受其他形式的嚴重傷害，或意圖抗拒或防止任何人受到合法拘捕或扣留而 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(a)以任何方式非法及惡意傷害任何人或導致任何人身體受嚴重傷害</span>；或<br />\n(b)向任何人射擊；或<br />\n(c)拉動扳機或以任何其他方式，企圖用上膛槍械向任何人發射，<br />\n即屬犯可循公訴程序審訊的罪行，可處終身監禁。</em>"},{"pid":"8a636d9bc4e6cb67832287df07e1510d62c805c3","tid":1822690,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"唉 可惜<br />\n當庭大叫支持警察或者可以無條件釋放"},{"pid":"3f370ffa1cfa3989fe16a592d9f5b98ca1663afe","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"全球第一宗巴士放針先兩年監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢2年6個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf512faf06d6b0da613290d153133bd23a37b26","tid":1822690,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a636d9bc4e6cb67832287df07e1510d62c805c3","tid":1822690,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"唉 可惜<br />\n當庭大叫支持警察或者可以無條件釋放"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"2017年案件應該唔受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884b2cd244a3c9c9c7601626ada6be041db6cdac","tid":1822690,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf512faf06d6b0da613290d153133bd23a37b26","tid":1822690,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a636d9bc4e6cb67832287df07e1510d62c805c3","tid":1822690,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"唉 可惜<br />\n當庭大叫支持警察或者可以無條件釋放"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"2017年案件應該唔受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb4c56d248681924e0ac5df36e42aa836c7d035","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"男子瑞和街網吧遭刀煞按地斬手腳 警查半日拘2漢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/789052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/789052</a><br />\n<br />\n當年新聞"},{"pid":"a81d4fc9c2ecd45ff4dd12d47aabc6a43e908682","tid":1822690,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"李柱銘個仔做辯方大狀, 係咪手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c80233e61181ebe94da49f31f34d0e660363cdc","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"另一男子(姓蔡26歲男子)點解冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f337e33d79d845e2d4de982acdf64098f47dc78","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"瑞和街發生傷人案 七人車網吧外遭2車截停扑車窗 司機捱斬<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/919635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/919635</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街街市4食客瑣事嘈交 互毆俱傷<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/996075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/996075</a>"},{"pid":"11398d43ff3c20db5aaabc54efaacc95cc5562fb","tid":1822690,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf512faf06d6b0da613290d153133bd23a37b26","tid":1822690,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a636d9bc4e6cb67832287df07e1510d62c805c3","tid":1822690,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"唉 可惜<br />\n當庭大叫支持警察或者可以無條件釋放"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"2017年案件應該唔受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"受佔中影響壓力大啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410b715edcb784cc0d734127f22f4b7212bccb96","tid":1822690,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"咁撚好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電競中心"},{"pid":"eb883f3eec866c0c87cbdb4f7e2dce7f70f87c6e","tid":1822690,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"練rank叫電競自修室好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60a60a1da7d6c2a25724f615c7dc5bb51e28c8c","tid":1822690,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410b715edcb784cc0d734127f22f4b7212bccb96","tid":1822690,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"咁撚好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電競中心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"收貴幾倍既網吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc4eb8fa476d7c409b9e243670b94754ec93657","tid":1822690,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"反修例示威持續，上月有中學生及校友築人鏈期間發生衝突。65歲退休漢於9月9日在文理書院（九龍）外指罵師生及揮動鎅刀，導致一名女教師手部受傷送院；案情指出，女教師事後要縫6針處理。退休漢今（11日）於觀塘裁判法院承認一項傷人罪，被判囚兩個月。裁判官表示，案發時逾80人組人鏈及叫口號，相信被告獨自面對他們才感害怕，是一時衝動所為。<br />\n<br />\n認罪的被告符柱標（65歲）報稱已退休和居於啟晴邨，控罪指他於2019年9月9日，在牛頭角沐虹街文理書院（九龍）外，非法及惡意傷害杜珮瑜。控方在庭上透露被告有26項案底，當中9項在暴力有關。辯方則指出，被告大部分案底和毒品有關，而上次涉傷人的案件發生於2002年。<br />\n<br />\n法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fb36a260903406a62c38bd4db9fbb62729f235","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a81d4fc9c2ecd45ff4dd12d47aabc6a43e908682","tid":1822690,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"李柱銘個仔做辯方大狀, 係咪手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"主控馬詠璋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[url]http://203.80.0.224/pdf_district/20140124/HLD20140124.A01-4C.PDF[/url]<br />\n非本地高等及專業教育上訴委員會 主席<br />\n上訴審裁團(建築物) 成員(成員 ︰每小時 875 元)<br />\n漁民特惠津貼上訴委員會 成員(每次出席會議 1,020 元)<br />\n土地及建設諮詢委員會 非官方成員<br />\n公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會 前成員"},{"pid":"dba40de163bab31399ac692e3d633aa6784de424","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5fb36a260903406a62c38bd4db9fbb62729f235","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a81d4fc9c2ecd45ff4dd12d47aabc6a43e908682","tid":1822690,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"李柱銘個仔做辯方大狀, 係咪手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"主控馬詠璋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[url]http://203.80.0.224/pdf_district/20140124/HLD20140124.A01-4C.PDF[/url]<br />\n非本地高等及專業教育上訴委員會 主席<br />\n上訴審裁團(建築物) 成員(成員 ︰每小時 875 元)<br />\n漁民特惠津貼上訴委員會 成員(每次出席會議 1,020 元)<br />\n土地及建設諮詢委員會 非官方成員<br />\n公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會 前成員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n<br />\n《學術及職業資歷評審條例》之下的上訴委員會 副主席<br />\n(每次出席會議 1,020 元 )"},{"pid":"c70062b0f1ac3e706827b9d8f2fbc01885d2aa0f","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a636d9bc4e6cb67832287df07e1510d62c805c3","tid":1822690,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"唉 可惜<br />\n當庭大叫支持警察或者可以無條件釋放"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:35:19.000Z","msg":"鄭念慈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n24歲女醫護下班獨自返回筲箕灣東熹苑寓所，在行經連接屋苑天橋時遭人用麻繩從後勒頸，事主拚命反抗，最後將歹徒按地及有途人幫手制服。被捕的21歲男學生葉溢銘承認一項企圖導致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪，今日(26日)在東區法院被判監8個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時指控罪性質及案情嚴重，被告用麻繩勒事主頸，只幸有途人及時揭發，才沒對事主造成更大傷害，即使被告初犯，唯一判刑選擇就只有即時監禁。"},{"pid":"840480e3a00ecf821eba93207e39fade5a6f4ba1","tid":1822690,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b60a60a1da7d6c2a25724f615c7dc5bb51e28c8c","tid":1822690,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410b715edcb784cc0d734127f22f4b7212bccb96","tid":1822690,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"咁撚好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電競中心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"收貴幾倍既網吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset